if maybe you wanted to come.

15:31.290 --> 15:33.510
I mean, I guess that
wouldn't totally suck.

15:33.560 --> 15:36.080
Cool, man.
I'd really like that.

15:36.130 --> 15:37.960
Burgers?
Okay, you know what?

15:38.000 --> 15:41.910
Music is one thing,
but a meat-related outing?

15:41.960 --> 15:44.000
Have fun
with your new best friend, Clay.

15:44.050 --> 15:46.830
It's an awesome ride,
but be warned.

15:46.870 --> 15:49.010
As soon as someone shiny and new
comes along,

15:49.050 --> 15:50.660
