light-headed, honey?

16:41.150 --> 16:42.710
Yeah, no, why would he
be light-headed?

16:42.760 --> 16:45.720
Oh, Andy, Fiona told me not
to say anything, but I have to.

16:45.760 --> 16:48.540
No, I know, I know, I know,
and I just wanted to say

16:48.590 --> 16:50.940
thank you so much
for enrolling me

16:50.980 --> 16:52.070
in magic school.

16:52.110 --> 16:53.420
Fiona told me, honey.

16:53.460 --> 16:55.330
