in magic school.

16:55.380 --> 16:56.940
We don't have any money.

16:56.990 --> 16:58.550
Isn't that why
you're donating your plasma?

16:58.600 --> 17:00.770
Honey, why would
I donate my plasma?

17:00.820 --> 17:03.300
Because--
Fiona said--

17:03.340 --> 17:05.080
Wait.
Fiona said--

17:05.130 --> 17:06.390
Well...
[clears throat]

17:06.430 --> 17:08.560
- The thing is--
- Oh, I know what the thing is.

17:08.610 --> 17:10.130
I know.

17:10.180 --> 17:12.530
You wanted a quick fix so that
we would get back together,

17:12.570 --> 17:14.480
have the baby,
and then you could get

17:14.530 --> 17:16.010
your stupid
doula certification.

17:16.050 --> 17:17.400
Well, you know what?

17:17.440 --> 17:19.140
You can't play
with people's lives

17:19.180 --> 17:20.660
for your own
selfish needs, Fiona.

17:20.710 --> 17:23.620
Well, I mean,
I do really, really want

17:23.670 --> 17:25.580
my doula certificate.

17:25.630 --> 17:27.720
I-I mean,
it was maybe a bit selfish,

17:27.760 --> 17:30.370
but--but the other thing
that's going on here

17:30.410 --> 17:32.890
is that you're too busy
fighting to realize

17:32.940 --> 17:36.110
how incredibly lucky you are
to have each other.

17:36.160 --> 17:39.030
Do you know where Marcus's dad
was when he was being born?

17:39.070 --> 17:40.730
He was in Antarctica.

17:40.770 --> 17:41.950
Yeah, he wanted
to stay there

17:41.990 --> 17:43.770
and watch the birth
of an albino penguin

17:43.820 --> 17:46.470
rather than see the birth
of his own child.

17:46.520 --> 17:51.090
I would have loved to have
someone who loved me by my side,

17:51.130 --> 17:52.610
and the fact
that you're choosing

17:52.650 --> 17:56.570
not to be with each other
is a bit of a slap in the face

17:56.610 --> 17:59.270
for those of us that didn't
actually have a choice.

18:07.410 --> 18:08.450
Honey.

18:08.490 --> 18:09.630
She's right.

18:09.670 --> 18:10.800
I know.

18:10.840 --> 18:12.630
We're so lucky
to have each other.

18:12.670 --> 18:14.150
We have each other.

18:14.200 --> 18:18.110
We may drive each other crazy,
but we have each other.

18:20.640 --> 18:22.680
- I love you.
- I love you too.

18:24.340 --> 18:25.640
[groaning loudly]

18:25.690 --> 18:27.570
It's happening!
Doula!

18:27.600 --> 18:28.510
Doula!

18:28.560 --> 18:29.510
Let's remember--

18:29.560 --> 18:30.910
- Help!
- It's coming!

18:30.950 --> 18:32.000
