Right, right, right.

18:32.040 --> 18:33.000
Now!

18:33.040 --> 18:36.700
Turn your "ow"
into "wow."

18:36.740 --> 18:37.700
[woman]
There you go.

18:37.740 --> 18:42.480
[both]
Waah!

18:42.530 --> 18:45.660
