a more natural fit for you.

19:24.660 --> 19:26.440
I've never seen
the top of the backboard

19:26.490 --> 19:27.670
down onto the rim.

19:27.700 --> 19:30.050
[grunts]
You know,

19:30.100 --> 19:31.750
