to Liz that I get to know him.

19:49.680 --> 19:54.430
Wait, this whole thing today,
it was--it was for Liz?

19:54.470 --> 19:56.730
Yeah, of course.

19:56.780 --> 19:57.690
- Hey.
- Oh, hey.

19:57.730 --> 19:59.260
